name: Kids Electric Car
description: Electric cars are cars which are electrically charged at the charging station, so they do not need petrol. Lightweight and efficient lithium ion batteries can keep the car running 100 km with a speed of 80 km/hour. Some electric cars can even give you an estimate of how far they can travel that day!

name: JBL Go 3 Portable Bluetooth Speaker
description: JBL Go 3 is IP67 waterproof and dustproof, so you can bring your speaker anywhere. Wirelessly stream music from your phone, tablet, or any other Bluetooth-enabled device. JBL Go 3 gives you up to 5 hours of playtime on a single charge.
